Third-party / vendored components

GateLab bundles the D3-based plotting modules from GateLabR
(vendor/GateLabR/inst/app/www/*.js — cytof_plot.js, mini_plot.js,
division_plot.js, d3.v7.min.js) and reimplements GateLabR's R analysis engine
in TypeScript. GateLabR is distributed under the MIT License, also
Copyright (c) 2026 David G. Priest; its original license text is retained at
vendor/GateLabR/LICENSE. d3.v7.min.js is Copyright Mike Bostock, released under
the ISC License.
